snippet.title: How Paul George Used Kobe Bryant as His Guide in Becoming an NBA Star
snippet.description: If you're Kobe Bryant , it's an awkward time. You've never been further from where you want to be, you've never had less time to get there and you've never been more uncertain if your body will let you even try...
